on|date=26 October 2012|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2015-05-22|archive-date=2012-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121028183614/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/20095041|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

